# Project overview (fizz5)

Codename: `fizz5`

## Repository intent

`fizz5.webflow/` is a Webflow export used only as a design reference. New code lives under `src/` and is hosted via a single Cloudflare Worker.

## Default engineering style

- Small PRs.
- Conventional Commits.
- TypeScript-first for new code.
- Avoid copying Webflow runtime artifacts unless absolutely needed.
